==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: named
<hw>named</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>given or having a
specified name; <as>as, an actor <ex>named</ex> Harold Lloyd; a building
in Cardiff <ex>named</ex> the Temple of Peace</as>. Contrasted to
<ant>unnamed</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> called.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>bearing the author's name; <as>as, a <ex>named</ex>
source</as>. Opposite of <ant>anonymous</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>namedrop</ent>⟦br⟧
